Title: JET Range 806 safety valve set 15mm 6.0bar

Title: Liff Limebeater electrolytic filter 28mm
Description: A simple solution for limescale issues, the Liff Limebeater 28mm electrolytic scale inhibitor uses the electrolytic principle to minimise the damage and mess caused by limescale. Inducing an electromagnetic field, the Limebeater changes the way scale forms by altering the alignment of mineral molecules during crystalline formation. This way, molecules choose to form long chains, developing into narrow, sharp crystals, commonly called aragonite. This long, thin shape means aragonite is less likely to form the hard, insulating scale that calcite can, making cleaning easier.

Title: Hattersley FIG. 33X gate valve (BSP) PN20 50mm Bronze
Description: This Hattersley 33X gate valve includes 2" BSP tapered female connections.  A gate valve, also known as a sluice valve, opens by lifting a barrier out of the path of a fluid. Gate valves normally require minimal space along the pipe axis and offer minimal flow restriction when fully open. A multiturn valve, operation of a gate valve is carried out via a threaded stem, turning multiple times to change position. Hattersley valves offer a straight through design providing reduced resistance to flow while keeping pressure drop to a minimum. Gate valves are not recommended for throttling and subsequent damage due to erosion may prevent the valve providing an effective shut-off.

Title: Inta vent auto air eliminator deaerator 22mm
Description: The inline Inta Vent 22mm auto air eliminator deaerator is designed to solve the issue of trapped air in sealed systems. It operates by generating a vortex when fluid enters the unit's base through a coil of stainless steel mesh, on which microbubbles form. These bubbles then combine and rise to the top of the filter where they can be removed via the air vent. Resistant to corrosion and component wear, this automatic air eliminator is designed for long lasting reliability.

Title: Grundfos Magna 3 D 32-120 F 220 circulating pump 1 x 230V PN6/10
Description: Ideal for creating high performance heating and cooling systems, the Grundfos MAGNA3 32 - 120 F single phase circulator pump is suitable for new installations and refits, offering excellent efficiency and built-in communication capabilities. With a canned rotor, this pump is a maintenance-free integral unit with no shaft seal and just two gaskets for sealing, while bearings are lubricated by the pumped liquid. Wirelessly connecting with the Grundfos GO Remote app, for advanced reporting and monitoring, MAGNA3 is suitable for mixing loops, heating and air conditioning surfaces, ground source heat pumps and small chillers and includes fieldbus communication via CIM modules as well analogue and digital inputs and configurable relays. Title: Wilo Stratos Maxo-D R7 40/0.5-8 PN6/10 twin head commercial pump
Description: The Wilo Stratos Maxo-D R7 is an easy to use smart pump with one touch commisioning, EC motor, electronic power adjustment and permanent, automatic performance adaptation for optimum energy efficiency. The R7 version does not include an internal temperature sensor.  This twin head smart-pump has a range of functions for reliable use including heating and cooling quantity measurement, dry running detection and automatic No-Flow Stop, which deactivates the pump when no flow is detected.  Each pump operates individually with one main pump and one pump on standby, meaning if any faults are detected the pumps will automatically switch over to prevent failure.  This is an inline glandless pump, suitable to be used in domestic or light commercial buildings for all central heating, cooling, underfloor heating, water/glycol mixtures and air conditioning systems.
